### ==== AUDIT API ====
# Docs: http://localhost:5000/scalar/v1
# Base routes:
#   /api/v1/audit                    — audit logs + statistics
#   /api/v1/admin/login-audit        — login attempt audit
#   /api/v1/admin/rtbf-requests      — Right-to-be-Forgotten (Law 91/2025)
#   /api/v1/admin/incidents          — security incident tracking (QĐ742)

# ── Audit Logs ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Query audit logs (paged, optional filters)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/audit/logs?page=1&pageSize=20
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Query audit logs with filters (date range + module + action)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/audit/logs?tenantId={{tenantId}}&from=2026-01-01T00:00:00Z&to=2026-12-31T23:59:59Z&moduleName=Cases&action=Create&page=1&pageSize=20
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Query audit logs for a specific user
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/audit/logs?userId=00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001&page=1&pageSize=20
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Query audit logs for a specific resource
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/audit/logs?resourceType=Case&resourceId=00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001&page=1&pageSize=20
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Get audit statistics (today/week/month counts, by action, by module)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/audit/statistics
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Get audit statistics for a specific tenant
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/audit/statistics?tenantId={{tenantId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

# ── Login Audit ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

###

### Query login attempts (all, paged)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/login-audit?page=1&pageSize=20
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Query failed login attempts in a date range
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/login-audit?success=false&from=2026-03-01T00:00:00Z&to=2026-03-14T23:59:59Z&page=1&pageSize=20
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Query login attempts for a specific user
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/login-audit?userId=00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001&page=1&pageSize=20
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

# ── RTBF Requests (Right-to-be-Forgotten) ───────────────────────────────────

###

### List RTBF requests (all statuses)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/rtbf-requests?page=1&pageSize=20
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### List pending RTBF requests for a tenant
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/rtbf-requests?tenantId={{tenantId}}&status=Pending&page=1&pageSize=20
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Process RTBF request (PII anonymization completed)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/rtbf-requests/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001/process
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "processedBy": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001"
}

###

### Reject RTBF request with reason
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/rtbf-requests/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001/reject
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "processedBy": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001",
  "reason": "Request does not meet criteria under Law 91/2025 Art. 9 — data retention required for active legal proceedings."
}

# ── Security Incidents (QĐ742) ───────────────────────────────────────────────

###

### List security incidents (all)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/incidents?page=1&pageSize=20
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### List open high-severity incidents
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/incidents?severity=High&status=Open&page=1&pageSize=20
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Report a new security incident
# Severity enum: Low, Medium, High, Critical
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/incidents
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "tenantId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001",
  "title": "Brute-force attempt detected on admin login",
  "description": "50+ failed login attempts from IP 192.168.1.100 within 5 minutes.",
  "severity": "High",
  "reportedBy": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001"
}

###

### Update incident status
# Status enum: Open, Investigating, Resolved, Closed
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/incidents/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001/status
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "Resolved",
  "mitigationNote": "IP blocked at WAF level. User accounts reviewed, no compromise found."
}
